00:26:00.110 --> 00:26:03.140
You may have created
new life in that drawer.

00:26:03.140 --> 00:26:06.120
And where's the fruit live?

00:26:06.120 --> 00:26:07.640
The side of it or
on the counter.

00:26:07.640 --> 00:26:08.360
Counter people?

00:26:08.360 --> 00:26:09.400
Where on the counter, though?

00:26:09.400 --> 00:26:10.130
Who said counter?

00:26:10.130 --> 00:26:10.640
In a bowl.

00:26:10.640 --> 00:26:11.556
