00:26:11.556 --> 00:26:12.380
Yeah.

00:26:12.380 --> 00:26:14.580
On top of the refrigerator
to keep it nice and warm.

00:26:14.580 --> 00:26:15.770
I like that.

00:26:15.770 --> 00:26:19.250
Or like behind in some corner,
