00:26:24.154 --> 00:26:25.070
AUDIENCE: [INAUDIBLE].

00:26:25.070 --> 00:26:27.890
LASZLO BOCK: Yeah,
and you've got

00:26:27.890 --> 00:26:29.892
that peach that's been there.

00:26:29.892 --> 00:26:31.850
It's been there long
enough that you don't even

00:26:31.850 --> 00:26:34.266
want to reach for it, because
