00:26:34.266 --> 00:26:36.850
sink into it.

00:26:36.850 --> 00:26:39.400
And then you throw it away.

00:26:39.400 --> 00:26:42.210
You want to eat better,
take the juice out.

00:26:42.210 --> 00:26:43.500
Take out the to-go containers.

00:26:43.500 --> 00:26:44.652
Take out all that stuff.

