there for 15 years,

00:49:13.980 --> 00:49:16.030
and Goldman Sachs have been,
all these other companies.

00:49:16.030 --> 00:49:17.904
So we had to invest and
build a relationship,

00:49:17.904 --> 00:49:20.070
so lesson one was
we went to places

00:49:20.070 --> 00:49:21.870
that we had not gone to before.

00:49:21.870 --> 00:49:23.640
