two components--

00:50:41.360 --> 00:50:44.090
intellectual
humility, which is--

00:50:44.090 --> 00:50:45.860
I mean you can have a
big ego and be here,

00:50:45.860 --> 00:50:49.250
but you have to be willing
to admit you're wrong when

00:50:49.250 --> 00:50:51.470
presented with new information.

00:50:51.470 --> 00:50:53.019
And the second is
conscientiousness,

00:50:53.019 --> 00:50:55.310
because if you look at the
science of what predicts job

00:50:55.310 --> 00:50:57.770
performance, the best
predictor is actually

00:50:57.770 --> 00:50:59.070
having them do the job.

00:50:59.070 --> 00:50:59.930
Duh.

00:50:59.930 --> 00:51:02.510
The next best is
cognitive ability.

00:51:02.510 --> 00:51:04.010
So how do they learn?

00:51:04.010 --> 00:51:06.530
And the best thing to add to
that is conscientiousness.

00:51:06.530 --> 00:51:07.820
Do they care about the
environment around them?

00:51:07.820 --> 00:51:09.070
Do they care about the people?

00:51:09.070 --> 00:51:12.320
The least important thing
was actual experience

00:51:12.320 --> 00:51:14.210
in the field and
expertise in the field,

00:51:14.210 --> 00:51:17.450
because it turns out if you
have those first things,

00:51:17.450 --> 00:51:20.150
you can develop that last thing.

00:51:20.150 --> 00:51:22.430
And then the other last
